thread.title: Janine Momasso

author: Janine Momasso
title: Janine Momasso
text: I was totally skeptical, & went in prepared to drive away in my vehicle in case they low-balled me or seemed shady. After a very hassle-free inspection of my car & title, they offered me $100 less than I wanted. I couldn't believe it... They basically offered me the amount I wanted in my head. I knew they were honest at that point, so needless to say...I was thrilled to sell my car. Carlos was great.
